tion,Simulation,skeletal muscle,Skeletal Muscle,Tomography X-ray Computed,Tomography X-Ray Computed,unspecified side effect,Unspecified Side Effect,validity,Validity,x-ray computed tomography,X-ray Computed Tomography}
