  keywords = {acute heart infarction,Acute Heart Infarction,Acute Myocardial Infarction,adult,Adult,adverse event,Adverse Event,aged,Aged,albumin,Albumin,area under the curve,Area Under The Curve,Article,artificial neural network,Artificial Neural Network,autacoid,Autacoid,biological marker,Biological Marker,Biomarkers,blood,Blood,cardiogenic shock,Cardiogenic Shock,cerebrovascular accident,Cerebrovascular Accident,cholesterol blood level,Cholesterol Blood Level,confidence interval,Confidence Interval,controlled study,Controlled Study,creatinine,Creatinine,decision support system,Decision Support System,Decision Support Techniques,decision tree,Decision Tree,diagnosis,Diagnosis,diagnostic test accuracy study,Diagnostic Test Accuracy Study,electronic medical record system,Electronic Medical Record System,etiology,Etiology,female,Female,heart arrest,Heart Arrest,heart death,Heart Death,heart failure,Heart Failure,heart infarction,Heart Infarction,heart left ventricle ejection fraction,Heart Left Ventricle Ejection Fraction,heart rate,Heart Rate,high density lipoprotein cholesterol,High Density Lipoprotein Cholesterol,human,Human,Humans,inflammation,Inflammation,Inflammation Mediators,Inflammatory Index,leukocyte count,Leukocyte Count,logistic regression analysis,Logistic Regression Analysis,low density lipoprotein cholesterol,Low Density Lipoprotein Cholesterol,lymphocyte count,Lymphocyte Count,machine learning,Machine Learning,Major Adverse Cardiovascular Event,major clinical study,Major Clinical Study,male,Male,malignant arrhythmia,Malignant Arrhythmia,malnutrition,Malnutrition,middle aged,Middle Aged,model,Model,monocyte count,Monocyte Count,monocyte lymphocyte ratio,Monocyte Lymphocyte Ratio,Myocardial Infarction,neutrophil count,Neutrophil Count,neutrophil lymphocyte ratio,Neutrophil Lymphocyte Ratio,Nutrition Assessment,nutritional assessment,Nutritional Assessment,nutritional status,Nutritional Status,outcome assessment,Outcome Assessment,percutaneous coronary 